summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 7406, entitled "An Ordinance providing for the improvement of the alley in Block 55, of Terry's First Addition to the City of Seattle, by building proper approaches to said alley from the adjoining streets; and providing for the payment therefor by the mode of "Immediate Payment," under the provisions of Ordinance No. 5693 of said city, approved December 6, 1899."
